Product Name: Dad's Hack Berry Basil Kombucha - Non-Alcoholic Drink, Boosts Energy, 330 ml
Product Description: Dad's Hack Kombucha is an ancient tea-based elixir reinvented with modern artisanal techniques that leave its consumers feeling relaxed and energized. It is a guilt-free, non-alcoholic drink that gives a boost of energy and also uplifts the mood. The naturally fermented drink is an ideal alternative to alcohol and soft drinks, allowing consumers to socialize and unwind without worrying about a buzz or hangover afterwards. Despite being low in calories, sugar, and caffeine, Dad's Hack Kombucha still has enough flavourr to be refreshing and healthy. Furthermore, the drink is excellent for gut health, the mind, and liver detoxification since it is naturally carbonated, devoid of preservatives and chemicals, and packed with vitamins, probiotics, and amino acids. The drink can be taken first thing in the morning for its detoxifying effect, in the middle of the day for an easy pick-me-up, or mixed with Gin for a whole new drink. A stimulating strawberry, blueberry & hibiscus booch subtly spiced with aromatic organic basil. It's a perfect rose for a family lunch and sundowners with friends.
